videoDetails.Title: A basic guide to line-ups. (low/mid tier) War Thunder.
videoDetails.Description:
Here is a new kind of video I'm testing out to see if people find it useful. 

This is a basic guide to winning more games with a balanced lineup.

These are the same principles I follow when playing low-mid tier matches :)

Let me know what you think!

Hope you enjoy it.

Tankonaut.
